| **Scaling complexity** | Incremental growth, pilot validation |
| **Regulatory fragmentation** | Early partnership, standards harmonization |
| **Public skepticism** | Radical transparency, observer mode |
| **Technical limitations** | Continuous R&D, academic collaboration |
| **Resource constraints** | Non-profit funding, member contributions |

